PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1778069461
OL,3,CAsylum seeker advanced towards police
OL,4,Cofficer with knife shouting "Allahu
OL,5,CAkbar"
OL,7,FAn asylum seeker allegedly advanced
OL,8,Ftowards a PSNI officer with a knife
OL,9,Fbefore shouting the Islamic
OL,10,Fproclamation "Allahu Akbar", a court
OL,11,Fheard on Monday.
OL,13,FThe officer was forced to draw his gun
OL,14,Fwhen Libyan national Hamza Banali, 24,
OL,15,Fconfronted him in the Holyland area of
OL,16,Fsouth Belfast at the weekend, a judge
OL,17,Fwas told.
OL,26,@lD@]OUmD@FO]rD@NOUrD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
