FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1778069461
OL,3,CAsylum seeker advanced towards police
OL,4,Cofficer with knife shouting "Allahu
OL,5,CAkbar"
OL,7,FBanali, of address at Farnham Street
OL,8,Fin the city, denies any religious or
OL,9,Fhate motivation behind an incident
OL,10,Flinked to reports of cars being
OL,11,Fdamaged in the area.
OL,13,FHe appeared at Belfast Magistrates'
OL,14,FCourt charged with possessing a bladed
OL,15,Farticle in a public place and
OL,16,Fresisting police.
OL,18,FOfficers went to Damascus Street late
OL,19,Fon Saturday night amid claims that a
OL,20,Fman was damaging parked cars with a
OL,21,Fknife.
OL,26,@lD@]OUmD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1778069461
OL,3,CAsylum seeker advanced towards police
OL,4,Cofficer with knife shouting "Allahu
OL,5,CAkbar"
OL,7,FBanali, who is originally from
OL,8,FTripoli, was approached after he
OL,9,Fmatched the description given of the
OL,10,Fperpetrator.
OL,12,F"He advanced towards the police,
OL,13,Fdrawing a short, bladed knife," an
OL,14,Finvestigating detective claimed.
OL,16,FA sergeant at the scene then drew his
OL,17,Fgun, telling him to drop the knife and
OL,18,Fget onto the ground.
OL,26,@lD@]OUmD@FO]tD@AOUuD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1778069461
OL,3,CAsylum seeker advanced towards police
OL,4,Cofficer with knife shouting "Allahu
OL,5,CAkbar"
OL,7,FWithin seconds Banali allegedly
OL,8,Fdiscarded the blade before being
OL,9,Fdetained and handcuffed.
OL,11,FAs he was being arrested he shouted
OL,12,F"Allahu Akbar", the Arabic phrase
OL,13,Fmeaning "God is greater", the court
OL,14,Fheard.
OL,16,FThe defendant was said to be so
OL,17,Faggressive that he had to be
OL,18,Fphysically restrained as officers
OL,19,Ftransported him into custody.
OL,26,@lD@]OUmD@FO]tD@AOUtD@NO]uD@IOUuD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1778069461
OL,3,CAsylum seeker advanced towards police
OL,4,Cofficer with knife shouting "Allahu
OL,5,CAkbar"
OL,7,F"During interviews he denied any hate
OL,8,For religious motivation," the
OL,9,Fdetective added.
OL,11,F"He alleged intoxication was the
OL,12,Fcause, and denied ever having the
OL,13,Fknife in his possession."
OL,15,FBanali has not been charged with
OL,16,Fcriminal damage to any of the cars on
OL,17,FDamascus Street.
OL,19,FBut police opposed bail amid claims
OL,20,Fthat he poses a risk to the public
OL,26,@lD@]OUmD@FO]oD@AOUpD@YO]sD@AOUuD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1778069461
OL,3,CAsylum seeker advanced towards police
OL,4,Cofficer with knife shouting "Allahu
OL,5,CAkbar"
OL,7,FDefence solicitor Aidan Carlin argued
OL,8,Fthat it was nothing more than an
OL,9,Falcohol-fuelled incident.
OL,11,F"He made comments while intoxicated,
OL,12,Fsadly like so many people who come
OL,13,Fbefore the courts," the lawyer
OL,14,Fsubmitted.
OL,16,F"He said things and behaved in a way
OL,17,Fthat he regrets."
OL,19,FMr Carlin described Banali as an
OL,20,Funemployed pizza chef currently
OL,21,Fseeking asylum in the United Kingdom.
OL,26,@lD@]OUmD@FO]sD@AOUuD@SO]xD@AOUyD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
