OL,3,CAsylum seeker advanced towards police
OL,4,Cofficer with knife shouting "Allahu
OL,5,CAkbar"
OL,7,FRefusing bail, however, District Judge
OL,8,FAmanda Brady cited the risks that he
OL,9,Fcould either re-offend or flee.
OL,11,FShe remanded Banali in custody to
OL,12,Fappear in court again on May 7.
